Package org.opensextant.giscore.events

Class SimpleField

java.lang.Object
org.opensextant.giscore.events.SimpleField
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, IDataSerializable
public class SimpleField extends Object implements IDataSerializable, Serializable
A descriptor for a given schema field. A given field is described by its type, name and display name. The display name dictates (for some formats) how the field should be shown to the user. A SimpleField only exists in a Schema context.

DRAND
